query:
SELECT id, version, title, isLatest, isPrerelease, downloadCount, fileSizeMb, 
  LEFT(downloadUrlWindows, 80) as windowsUrl,
  LEFT(downloadUrlMac, 80) as macUrl,
  LEFT(downloadUrlLinux, 80) as linuxUrl
FROM releases ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5;
